airman to the National Assembly.\n\nWith this decision, the search for a candidate for the post of finance minister has started in the ruling NCP.\n\nAccording to sources, Vice Chairman Gautam, General Secretary Bishnu Paudel, Standing Committee members Janardan Sharma and Surendra Padey are in the fray for the post of Finance Minister.","title":"Cabinet meeting taking place at 11 am; FinMin Khatiwada resigning - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/04/124863/","video":[]}
